{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">BrightGunner\u00a0is a  innovative fast-paced first person shooter game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">simplicity and refreshment, the three major design concepts are: diversified gameplay, mild Rogue mechanism, and no interface design style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Diversified gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a multi-game mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In survival mode, players face an infinite number of waves of battles, each of which includes a large number of monsters and a light meat pigeon mechanic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The standard mode is a mix of multiple gameplay styles with multiple small levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition, there are five modes, Encounter, Sniper Battle, Boss Battle, Maze Exploration, and Story Mode. Each mode has its own focus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Mild Rogue mechanism</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monsters, cards and props appear randomly in the level, and a large number of monsters rush to the protagonist, and the protagonist's ability gradually grows. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players need to keep moving to avoid monsters and counterattacks, and search for supplies to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>No Interface design style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game replaces the traditional initial interface with an innovative initial scene, where game modes, levels, option settings, and skill upgrades are all completed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Player interacts by shooting bricks with a gun, instead of clicking buttons in the traditional interface.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3470190?t=1740411580","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3470190/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740411580","capsule_image":"h